-- Chinese Steel Stockpile Advanced 34% in First Quarter, Industry Group Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-04-28T01:08:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-28/chinese-steel-stockpile-advanced-34-in-first-quarter-industry-group-says.html

          
          
             Steel product stockpiles in China
rose 34.4 percent from the start of 2010 to the end of March,
the China Iron & Steel Association said in a statement today.  
 Inventories were 10.74 million metric tons at the end of
March, the statement said.  
